reviewText:
A congressman's daughter's plans to blackmail rich men backfires on her and her two friends who must now secretly record their escapades with old congressmen for someone else.

Bad acting. Bad script. 2 stars for the nudity.

F-bomb, sex, and nudity (Tracy Tutor, Libby George, Daneen Boone -Adventures of Justine series)
On the plus side, perhaps the final nude scenes by Daneen Boone, who not long after curtailed her acting career.
